Mix stuffing mix and hot water just until moistened; set aside. Meanwhile, brown meat in large skillet; drain. Add peppers, tomatoes with their liquid, ketchup, dressing and chili powder to skillet. Bring to boil. Reduce heat to medium-low; cover. Simmer 5 min. or until peppers are crisp-tender. Top with prepared stuffing. Cover; simmer 3 min.